3. cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) - The use of a relay node with storage capabilities may involve distributed computing concepts. 
4. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) - The popularity distribution of cached files may be related to social network analysis. 
5. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) - The paper may involve security considerations related to caching and transmission of content in a wireless network.
